enerating latency spikes and errors related to unavailable regions. Since these issues are primarily rooted in `ProductCatalogService`, and the other downstream scenarios align with pre-existing logs and traced relationships, this supports the hypothesis.\n\n### JSON Output:\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"error_code_9005\",\n    \"region_unavailable\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"ProductCatalogService exhibits persistent latency spikes and region unavailability errors during the anomaly, impacting dependent services. No upstream or alternative root cause observed in the traces.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Significant latency anomaly ratios (e.g., 3.84x blowout) across 'frontend -> productcatalogservice' and 'checkoutservice -> productcatalogservice'; Frequent 'Region is unavailable' errors specifically tied to this service.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
